{"tid":2136198,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"小店疫市組外賣車隊自救  熟客表支持 一碗糖水百元運費","createTime":"2020-08-02T03:38:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T04:16:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f80e56cc6664dbdb7903eaef6a32ad531d534135","tid":2136198,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T03:38:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200802/FKAWBXTCSLC52SH6XOUDZ5AMPI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200802%2FFKAWBXTCSLC52SH6XOUDZ5AMPI%2F&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAndekL701Gi2Y7kfdl15EDb4%3D&h=b47e48a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200802%2FFKAWBXTCSLC52SH6XOUDZ5AMPI%2F&h=04cb02a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200802/FKAWBXTCSLC52SH6XOUDZ5AMPI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n小店疫市組外賣車隊自救 <br />\n熟客表支持 一碗糖水百元運費<br />\n<br />\n【武肺再爆發】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】上月初佐敦爆出「新發茶餐廳」染疫群組，令食肆林立的渡船角淪為死城，一街之隔的40年老店「糖水雄」生意大跌八成。政府推禁堂食令後，個案遍地開花，市民遍地開餐，灰塵、雨水及汗水成配菜，一餐飽飯變成一殼眼淚。糖水店少東指「與其等死，不如應戰」，決定自組外賣車隊自救，近日更與同區其他小店共享車隊，盼共渡難關。<br />\n<br />\n記者：潘婉鈴、翁鈺輝、梁德聰<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FPJIBO2GIKxSI3n7vnx3iQGYdDM=/1054x561/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LAKGCJ4CQ5YZ75SRBGEO5WLSRU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFPJIBO2GIKxSI3n7vnx3iQGYdDM%3D%2F1054x561%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLAKGCJ4CQ5YZ75SRBGEO5WLSRU.gif&h=673e35fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現時外賣團隊多達60人，其中約10人長駐店外。<br />\n<br />\n上周三實施全日禁堂食首晚，記者傍晚6時許到小店直擊，只見外賣定單紛至，顧客透過電話或短訊下單，員工隨即準備食物，完成後由少東阿傑以膠袋包裝，用紙貼上不同地區，再分發外賣員。油尖旺區交「步兵」或單車手，其餘地區則出動車手。目前外賣團隊達60人，有大學生、中學教師、音樂人等，最特別是一位律師熟客也多次助阿傑送外賣到寓所附近，「佢話反正順路，送完返屋企」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：亞博啟用收30患者 走廊漏水<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eNK9hlQumfL6b4Cz_uORAoL7M4Q=/349x275/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CDVTXTBW454CUW256WE3DCD7B4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeNK9hlQumfL6b4Cz_uORAoL7M4Q%3D%2F349x275%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCDVTXTBW454CUW256WE3DCD7B4.gif&h=b3f401bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n外賣服務按地區收費，最遠可到東涌、鴨脷洲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n沙冰變水 改良速遞<br />\n<br />\n上月初，佐敦渡船角「新發茶餐廳」三日內爆出六宗的士司機確診，掀起疫情第三波序幕，曾經越夜越精采的渡船角隨即淪死城。「咁多年來都未試過擔心無生意，𠵱家根本睇唔到前景」，糖水店創辦人高修雄（58歲）望着店內空凳，一臉愁容。他指3月底政府推限聚令，只准。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n政府本月初禁止晚上6時後堂食，糖水雄生意暴跌八成，周末只有3,000多元收入，是疫情以來首錄虧損。7月最後一。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n而政府7月29日推行夜晚也禁堂食，阿傑當日決定與區內小店共享車隊。。。。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"fea004c8c8204d39b88481d81bcf7737e39fbdb1","tid":2136198,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T03:39:54.000Z","msg":"。。。。。。jm9"},{"pid":"1d22f50e518bb05353b15ab1d1d99a60b04f52cf","tid":2136198,"uid":267942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T03:44:13.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">追究肺炎責任，賠償死傷者損失，幫手用中性路線宣揚出去，要人</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"24c346db9de9ae78f210bd27922efcfacaf0949d","tid":2136198,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T04:16:42.000Z","msg":"60人咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}